event1.Title: Music_Kick_Off
event1.Discription: The RHHS Music department-wide kickoff is HERE! Come and bring all of your music friends and join us for lots of food and group games next Thursday, September 21st in the cafeteria. Doors will open at 5:00 PM but the event starts 5:30, so come prepared with either a main dish(NOT dessert) OR a $5 fee if you want to enter! ðŸ¥³ðŸŽ¶
